name: Blog-127.0.0.1
tagline: My personal git blog where you can find small Java, Maven, Wildfly, Java EE, etc articles and examples
body:
### Welcome to Blog-127.0.0.1.
So what can you expect to find on this blog? I can promise you will not find recipes for buns or DIY dinning table even though i'm actually pretty to both things. You will find what I call small git blog's with examples with Maven, Java and Java EE examples baked from previous experience I have encountered with the different technologies
